52,"text":831},"2022-12-30 10:28:35","Git treats readme.md and README.md as the same file on macOS or Windows, so renaming silently does nothing. How to reproduce the trap and two clean ways to fix it.","md","en",{},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002Fgit-filename-case-sensitivity-fix","3",{"title":6,"description":856},false,"en\u002FGit\u002Fgit-filename-case-sensitivity-fix",[538,129,866],"Troubleshooting",null,"2022-02-13 15:10:00","\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F30\u002Fgit-filename-case-sensitivity-fix\u002F","NbsfDAVzlS-6YXZaaPfmw0ClFIVXdcZWDWRGH3N6pgs",{"newer":872,"older":876},{"url":873,"title":874,"date":875},"\u002Fen\u002Fgsap\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F02\u002Fgsap3-fx-12-control-animations\u002F","(12) Fun Frontend Effects With GSAP3 - Controlling Animations","2023-01-02 15:33:00",{"url":877,"title":878,"date":879},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2022\u002F12\u002F25\u002Fupload-files-to-firebase-storage-with-nodejs\u002F","Step-by-Step: Uploading Files to Firebase Storage with Node.js","2022-12-25 17:00:00",[881,886,890],{"url":882,"title":883,"date":884,"readingMinutes":885},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2026\u002F02\u002F26\u002Fgit-push-force-with-lease-better-than-force\u002F","A Safer Alternative to git push --force: git push --force-with-lease","2026-02-26 09:39:40","4",{"url":887,"title":888,"date":889,"readingMinutes":861},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2026\u002F01\u002F22\u002Fgit-default-branch-master-to-main\u002F","Git init Shows a master Branch Hint? Here's How to Set main as Default","2026-01-22 16:20:40",{"url":891,"title":892,"date":893,"readingMinutes":894},"\u002Fen\u002Fgit\u002F2026\u002F01\u002F21\u002Fgit-worktree-multiple-ai-agents-one-project\u002F","What Is Git Worktree? The Secret to Running Multiple AI Agents in One Project","2026-01-21 16:04:27","5",1784087325360]